PRESIDENT John Magufuli has appointed Diwani Athuman as the new Director General of Tanzania Intelligence and Security Services (TISS). He is replacing Dr Modestus Kipilimba, who will be assigned other duties, a statement released by State House today (Thursday, Sept 12, 2019), said. Prior to his new post, Diwani Athuman was Director General of the Prevention and Combating of Corruption Bureau (PCCB). Mr Athuman took oath of office today in Dar es Salaam, according to the statement.